@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v1
    v2 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.98 * v2 + 0.60)) * (wp.abs(v0 + 0.98) / (v1 + 0.20 / v2 + 0.64)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.45)))
    v0 = wp.abs((wp.abs(v2 + 0.69) * (v0 + 0.33 / v0 + 0.39)))
    data[tid] = v0
